@page "/"

<PageTitle>VHouse - Modern Vegan POS System</PageTitle>

<div class="welcome-section">
    <h1>🌱 Welcome to VHouse</h1>
    <p>
        The next-generation <strong>Clean Architecture</strong> vegan Point of Sale system that accelerates your business operations with modern design principles and enterprise-grade architecture.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-2 mb-8">
