            </div>
            <div class="card-subtitle">Enterprise-grade features and patterns</div>
        </div>
        
        <ul class="architecture-list">
            <li>
                <span style="color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: bold;">✅</span>
                <div>
                    <strong>Clean separation of concerns</strong>
                    <div style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: var(--spacing-1);">Modular and maintainable codebase</div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span style="color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: bold;">✅</span>
                <div>
                    <strong>CQRS pattern with MediatR</strong>
                    <div style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: var(--spacing-1);">Command Query Responsibility Segregation</div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span style="color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: bold;">✅</span>
                <div>
                    <strong>Repository and Unit of Work patterns</strong>
                    <div style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: var(--spacing-1);">Data access abstraction and consistency</div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span style="color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: bold;">✅</span>
                <div>
                    <strong>Health checks and security headers</strong>
                    <div style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: var(--spacing-1);">Production-ready monitoring and security</div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li>
                <span style="color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: bold;">✅</span>
                <div>
                    <strong>Dependency injection throughout</strong>
                    <div style="font-size: var(--font-size-sm); color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: var(--spacing-1);">Testable and loosely coupled design</div>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="grid grid-3">
