        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">
            <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">🚀</span>
            <span>Performance</span>
        </div>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
            Blazor Server with SignalR for real-time updates, optimized for speed and responsiveness.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">
            <span style="font-size: 1.5rem;">🔒</span>
            <span>Security</span>
        </div>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
